article_title: Chris Cuomo: 'Little Dignity Has Been Given to the Victims' – New Day
article_text:
"New Day's" Chris Cuomo joins Don Lemon from the MH17 crash site in Ukraine, noting that "the bodies are being collected" and "little dignity has been given to the victims."

Chris is live in eastern Ukraine this morning with updates at 6am ET on CNN.

You can see images he's captured on the ground HERE.

RELATED: Malaysia Airlines crash: Kerry lashes out at Russia over downed jet
